{
  "chapter": 72,
  "chapter_summary": "芮玮收到高莫野留赠的青丝与檀木盒，误以为野儿仍挂念自己，不顾高寿劝阻，急赴华山寻人。高寿告知野儿在华山为尼，高莫静虽心痛却劝父亲放手。芮玮遍寻华山十七座尼庵不得，最后遇到一位神秘老人。老人跟踪他多时，告知华山实有太华、少华之分，野儿所在的慈悲庵在少华山，清规极严禁止男子进入，需闯过三道关卡方能入内。老人指点芮玮以武功闯关，并叮嘱随机应变。芮玮感激之余赶往少华山。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "我在想，野儿也认出我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她一定在怪我，见了面为何还不告诉她存在世上，难道我就残酷如斯，还要她独个忍受故人已亡的痛苦，啊，我真该死，我应该告诉她，我仍在世上……\n\n“是啦！是啦！我蒙面见她，她虽认出了我，故作不知，她以为我变了心，相认徒增痛苦，所以，所以……”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你蒙面见野儿，并无不对，野儿身入空门，离开尘俗，就好像他凡相隔，再相见只有痛苦。\n\n“我说玺儿，你不要再徒自悲伤了，我知道你深爱野儿，现在你们两人，既不可能再以尘俗之身相聚，我劝你还是忘了她吧，野儿并不希望你再念念不忘于她。\n\n“你知不知道静儿很喜欢你，我与你父一场深交，你就好比我的亲子一般，我希望你能和静儿成婚，不要再浪迹江湖，安居在我身旁，这样也就不枝我与你父相交一场，玺儿，我这意思，你说好吗？”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "对啦，伯父，当年你在什么地方接回莫野妹？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "其实我虽勒令天下兵马打探你和野儿的下落，只知你的消息，并未打听到野儿的去向，还是野儿闻说我在寻找她的下落，从华山携信来说，她在华山为尼……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "华山？\n\n好！我这就去华山。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你去华山做什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "我去华山找野儿回来……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不能去！你不能去！华山不能去……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "爷，你让他去找二妹……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "不行，不行，华山他不能去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "静儿，你哭什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "我没哭啊？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你……你……都听到了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "他爱极二妹，此心不死，还是让他亲见二妹一面，知道二妹佛心后，自会好点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "可是你二妹修行处轻易不能去啊！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "佛庵圣地怎么不能去，爷，你放心，他武功不弱，不会吃亏的……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个他怎么不拿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shou",
      "speaker_name": "高寿",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "他只拿走你二妹的长发，这本书看也没看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_gao_shou",
      "text": "爷，这本书女儿暂且保管。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bi_qiu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "老尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "素心？\n\n老身就叫素心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ni",
      "text": "不！不！在下不是找你。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bi_qiu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "老尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这大冷天，随便敲门，这不是害人？\n\n活见鬼！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ni",
      "text": "老师父，庵内还有没有位叫素心的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bi_qiu_ni",
      "speaker_name": "老尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有个鬼！整个庵内再有一个人，就是鬼啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "内功，我服了你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "老文有何贵干？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这位小兄弟别怪我刚才无礼，我想试你来着，结果一试，大有可为。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "什么大有可为？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不是在找人吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "老文如何知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "华山共有十七座尼庵，打你从第一座尼庵找起，我就跟了你了。\n\n“老人不等芮玮疑问，接道：大冷天找人，而且找的是位尼姑，这尼姑对你想来十分重要，我好奇下，倒要看看这位尼姑是谁？\n\n“结果跟到最后一座尼庵，那老比丘发了火，你失望了，我也失望了。\n\n“你失望的表情令我很感动，本来我的失望很小，只是一种好奇没有结果的失望，看到你痛苦的表情，我觉得花了那么大的劲，跟着你，未能看到一位能令你——既年轻又有为的青年氦丧至斯的尼姑，大大不甘心起来。\n\n“我非要见见那位尼姑是谁，害得你如此，为了满足我强烈的好奇心，所以我想指给你一条明路……”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "敢情老文知道这华山上还有一座外人无法找到的尼庵？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "华山整座仅有一十七处尼庵，连你最后找到的小的可怚的尼庵，再无另外一座尼庵。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "什么？还有另一座华山？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你知不知道华山又名太华？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "啊！少华山！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为了有个区别，所以这两座华山，一个叫太华，一个叫少华，仅言华山可以笼统包括这两座山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "那我找错了地方，伯父指的华山是少华山。\n\n老文，请问少华山有没有尼庵？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有，而且你去找，不用再找第二家了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "怎么！少华山只有一座尼庵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，仅有一座，可是仅这一座够你麻烦了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "是不是这座尼庵难找，在少华山上十分隐秘处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不难找，你上少华山就可以发现。\n\n麻烦的，不是找的问题，而是你能不能进入那座尼庵，去问‘请问有没有位素心师姑？’",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "难道那座尼庵不准外人去进香吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "进香谈何容易，她们根本不受香火，你去时倘言找位尼姑，尤其像你这样年纪的人，只怕一辈子也别想进去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "这…这…是什么道理？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这道理很简单，慈悲庵的清规天下闻名，里面尼姑除了自己母亲可会外，别说普通男人就是父亲也不准见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "那…那…怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "所以我要试你一试，大有可为是说你既有深厚的内力，武功是不会错的，武功好就简单了……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "武功好与进那慈悲庵有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "慈悲庵为示铁律一般的清规所以戒绝访客，可是能阻止访客硬冲吗？\n\n“她们不怕硬冲的客人，定下一条规矩，能冲三道关，慈悲庵任你进来。\n\n“可是若言找庵内的年轻尼姑，三道关就是闯过也不准见，除非你先杀光全庵的尼姑，最后剩下你要见的尼姑，到那时候无人阻止，只得让你们痛痛快快地相见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "多谢老文指点。若非老文细言，在下茶撞，只怕这生再无法一见野儿。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你那情侣叫野儿吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "你可千万要小心了，到慈悲庵受阻拦时，你就说闯关两字，闯了关再随机应变，切记！\n\n“切记！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "多谢老文指点。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你快点去吧，祝你顺利，成不成功，千万不要气鞒，诚之所致，金石为开，天下没有办不成的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "text": "老文姓名可否见告？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "神秘老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我帮你只是好奇，并不希望你记恩，何必把我姓名记在心头，再说我的姓名很久不用，早已忘了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
